# Review Agent Rules

Block merge if:

- Feature imports another feature.
- Product cards load GLB/USDZ/model-viewer.
- 3D has no 15s timeout/fallback.
- Admin JWT is stored in localStorage.
- Admin mutations lack CSRF header/validation.
- Backend accepts arbitrary `specsJson`.
- Media upload bypasses pre-upload/backend validation.
- R2 upload has no confirm flow.
- Media reorder is missing.
- API path lacks `/api/v1`.
- API diverges from `openapi.yaml`.
- Prisma schema changed without migration.
- Product color/site_settings tables are added in Phase 1 without re-scope.


Also block merge if:

- English UI copy appears in public/admin UI without Human approval.
- Validation/toast/fallback messages are not Vietnamese.
- SEO metadata defaults are English.


Also block merge if:

- Mobile/tablet layout is broken.
- Horizontal scroll appears at 360/390/430/768/1024px.
- Admin UI is desktop-only.
- Product detail CTA is not reachable on mobile.
- Responsive requirements in `MOBILE_RESPONSIVE_REQUIREMENTS.md` are ignored.


Also block merge if:

- Android/iOS mobile browser rules are ignored.
- iOS input zoom issue appears due to small input font.
- Sticky bottom CTA ignores iPhone safe area.
- Mobile upload requires drag-and-drop.
- Critical action is hover-only.
- AR has no iOS/Android fallback.
